Step 3 granular UI canon obligation (`feedback_long_running_progress_heartbeat_canon_bp078`) remains open until Founder confirms the fix works on a REAL fresh download (prior v0.1.41 verify was source-only; canon requires actual runtime evidence per `feedback_actual_runtime_verify_for_runtime_bugs_bp078`).

